# mcp-package/skills.list — curated manifest of skills shipped in the clade-mcp
# PyPI package. mcp-package/skills/ is a DERIVED copy of configs/skills/:
# edit skills under configs/skills/, then run:
#
#   configs/scripts/regen-mcp-package.sh
#
# CI diffs a fresh regeneration against the committed copy and fails on drift.
